<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <title>Percentage Margins in Shrink Wrap Blocks</title>
  <link rel="author" title="Ian Hickson" href="mailto:ian@hixie.ch"/>
  <link rel="alternate" href="http://www.hixie.ch/tests/adhoc/css/box/block/013.html"/>
  <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/visudet.html#the-width-property"/>
  <style type="text/css">
   body, html { margin: 0 0 0 1em; padding: 0; }
   p { margin: 1em 0; height: 2em; }
   table, .float, .abspos, .fixpos { border: 0.25em solid; background: red; }
   table, td { padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; }
   .float { float: left; }
   .fixpos { position: fixed; left: 7.5em; top: 4em; }
   .abspos { position: absolute; left: 7.5em; top: 9.5em; }
   .test { margin: 20%; width: 5em; height: 5em; background: green; }
  </style>
 </head>
 <body>
  <p>There should be four green squares below making a green square pattern.</p>
  <table><tbody><tr><td>
   <div class="test"></div>
  </td></tr></tbody></table>
  <div class="float">
   <div class="test"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="fixpos">
   <div class="test"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="abspos">
   <div class="test"></div>
  </div>
 

</body>
</html>
